source: A passenger door has become stuck. Indentify and manually operate the door to unstick it.
Translation: 乘客侧车门卡住了。请找到该车门并手动操作，使其脱离卡住状态。

source: AWS has forced a penalty brake, reset AWS and wait until penalty duration times out to begin taking power again.
Translation: AWS 已强制执行惩罚性制动，将重置 AWS 并等待惩罚持续时间结束后再开始恢复供电。

source: Battery power must be turned on to power the cab and enable the controls on the drivers desk.
Translation: 必须打开电池电源才能为驾驶室供电并启用驾驶员桌上的控制装置。

source: Come to a full stop and press the Power Reduction button to disable Power Reduction.
Translation: 完全停止后，按下“降低功率”按钮即可关闭降低功率功能。

source: Driver Safety Device is in emergency, bring train to a stop and use vigilance pedal to clear this Emergency Brake
Translation: 驾驶员安全装置处于紧急状态，请将列车停下并使用警戒踏板解除紧急制动。
EMK 350/3 型列车 [4 节车厢]

source: Insert and set the Master Key to ON and set the Reverser away from OFF to activate this cab.
Translation: 插入主钥匙并将其设置为 打开，并将换向器从 关闭 位置移开，即可激活此驾驶室。
乐器 + 桌子 + 时间表

source: Move the Power Brake Controller to OFF and then set the DRA to OFF to disable the DRA.
Translation: 将动力制动控制器移至“关闭”位置，然后将 DRA 设置为“关闭”以禁用 DRA。

source: Select AC or DC power mode by pressing AC/DC Power, then turn the Panto/VCB switch to Up/On to close breakers.
Translation: 按 AC/DC Power 选择 AC 或 DC 电源模式，然后将 PaNTo/VCB 开关拨到 Up/打开 位置以闭合断路器。

source: Set the Reverser away from OFF to activate this cab.
Translation: 将换向器从“关闭”位置移开，即可激活此驾驶室。

source: Set the direction of travel to FORWARD or REVERSE before applying power.
Translation: 接通电源前，请将行驶方向设置为前进或后退。

source: The TPWS fuse has tripped, bring the train to a stop then reset the fuse.
Translation: TPWS保险丝跳闸了，请将列车停下，然后重置保险丝。

source: The Windshield Wiper appears to have become stuck.
The pantograph is blocked. Bring the train to a stop and try dropping the pantograph then raising it again.
Translation: 受电弓被卡住了。请将列车停下，然后尝试放下受电弓再将其升起。

source: This passenger door has been unstuck.
Translation: 这扇乘客侧车门已经修好了。

source: Traction lock will not release while the passenger doors are open or unlocked.
Translation: 当乘客侧车门打开或解锁时，牵引力锁不会解除。

source: Traction lock will not release whilst either cab door is open.
Translation: 当驾驶室任一车门打开时，牵引锁将不会解除。

Translation: 西海岸干线：伯明翰新街至克鲁

source: Denied. Dispatcher is unable to authorize movements.
Translation: 已拒绝。调度员无法授权此次调动。

source: Denied. Move up to the signal and wait.
Translation: 已拒绝，请前进至信号灯处等待

source: Denied. Service not authorized in signalled area.
Translation: 拒绝。信号区域内未授权提供服务。
已拒绝，前方区段有列车

source: Denied. Wait for signal to change.
Translation: 已拒绝，请等待信号改变

source: Denied. Your train appears to be off path.
Translation: 已拒绝，您的列车似乎偏离了预定轨道
